Basic retrieval: retrieve results of a query. No binding.
  Input: none
  Output: result set

For every reference field for entity A:
  - Bind reference query. For each field, find which entity field belongs to
  - All fields that are not belonging to A are to be bound
  - The node for every bound field should keep a field list for fields that will be used for evaluating bindings
     
     

